## Cost Management & Estimation

Even though you are using VS Code Chat (which may be "unlimited" in your subscription tier), the underlying model usage still matters. The original tool tracks **premium requests** because the CLI `copilot -p` consumes them. In a chat environment, you can still apply the **planning discipline** to avoid wasting tokens.

- **Pre‑execution Estimator**: Predicts number of agent invocations based on plan steps and historical failure rates.
- **Budgeting**: Set a hard limit on number of chat rounds per session.
- **Cost Attribution**: Keep a log of which agent consumed how many interactions.

